Package components.waypointcard

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IWaypointCard<WP extends AbstractWaypoint>
    This interface describes a component displaying informations about a waypoint (DeliveryAddress or Warehouse)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeliveryAddressCard
    This component is a wrapper for a delivery address, it is show in the Planning Details Pane at the right of the canvas
    EditableDeliveryAddressCard
    The EditableDeliveryAddressCard represents the form to enter a new waypoint.
    WarehouseCard
    The WarehouseCard component is able to display data about a warehouse in a small rectanlge (card).
    WaypointCard
    This component is a wrapper for a DeliveryAddressCard or WarehouseCard.
    WaypointCardBase<WP extends AbstractWaypoint>
